{"id":624328971,"lang":"java","time":"1 month, 1 week","timestamp":1642732648,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"2 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/624328971/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Divide Two Integers","memory":"38.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int divide(int dividend, int divisor) {\n        if (dividend == Integer.MIN_VALUE && divisor == -1) return Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n        \n        boolean isNegative = (dividend >= 0) == (divisor >= 0) ? false : true;\n        dividend = Math.abs(dividend);\n        divisor = Math.abs(divisor);\n        \n        int result = 0;\n        while (dividend - divisor >= 0) {\n            int count = 0;\n            while (dividend - (divisor << 1 << count) >= 0) {\n                // System.out.println(\"divisor \" + divisor);\n                // System.out.println((1 << count) + \" \" + (divisor << count));\n                // System.out.println((divisor << 1 << count));\n                count++;\n            }\n            result += (1 << count);\n            dividend -= (divisor << count);\n        }\n        return isNegative ? -result : result;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"divide-two-integers"}
